songs.title: Save Yourself
songs.lyrics:
[Big Krizz Kaliko]
You can't get my money ho, you're scheming on my wealth
How about getting a j-o-b then you can save yourself
I don't know why these hoes are always in my face for money
Grant Rice, Kutt, and Tech N9ne said save yourself, save yourself
Grant Rice, Kutt, and Tech N9ne said save yourself
(Applause)
